  {
    "hotel_id": "8829400",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/belmont-hotel-boracay/hotel/boracay-island-ph.html",
    "name": "Belmont Hotel Boracay near Newcoast Beach",
    "detail": "My family and I stayed here when a Category 3 typhoon hit Boracay on Christmas Day and flattened most of the island, many lost their homes and power. We however felt so lucky to have a room at the Belmont where we never lost electricity, the staff were so helpful and provided us with whatever we needed, and never stopped smiling. The breakfast buffets are great. Special mention goes to staff at the Belmont Cafe including Fernan and MJ who were always caring, friendly and good for a nice chat, but all the staff were most attentive and excellent. The facilities here are superb, the rooms are extremely clean, and the location is at a very peaceful part at Boracay Newcoast. The Belmont provides free shuttle services to D'Mall which were very handy. Overall we totally enjoyed our 2 week stay at the Belmont, storms and all, this is the best place to be. Hope to be back soon! 10/10. ",
